<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/catherine-mckinnell> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Catherine McKinnell was previously Minister of State (Minister for School Standards) at the Department for Education between 8 July 2024 and 6 September 2025. She was elected as the Labour MP for Newcastle Upon Tyne North in May 2010."@en .
